        "testimonial-1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Partnering with Pacific Coast Roasters has elevated our coffee program in all the right ways. The quality is consistently exceptional, and each offering feels intentional, like it was chosen with real care behind it.\n\nWhat we appreciate most is their ability to bring something unique without losing approachability. Our customers trust it, come back for it, and genuinely enjoy exploring what’s new.\n\nIt’s rare to find a roaster that balances craft, consistency, and creativity this well. Pacific Coast Roasters has been an easy and valuable addition to what we do at Lito’s.",
